paths: Obvious exits: north, southeast, south, southwest, west
description: Plum trees thrive in the middle of the central hall.  Freely growing Imaera's lace and other creeping vines obscures most of the walls of the airy chamber.  Individual beds of various plants and bushes are scattered throughout, creating a tranquil setting.
title: [The Cobbler's Cobby, Atrium]
